body:
On `Verilator 4.026 2020-01-11 rev v4.026-2-g0c6c83e2` the code below gives me an internal error.

```
`default_nettype none
/* verilator lint_off DECLFILENAME */

module unlinkbug(input i, output o);
  bug b(i, o);
endmodule

module bug(input i, output o);
  assign o = (i===1'bz) ? 1'b0 : i;
endmodule
```

```
docker run -ti -v ${PWD}:/work --user $(id -u):$(id -g) verilator/verilator:latest -Wall --lint-only unlinkbug.v

%Error: Internal Error: unlinkbug.v:5: ../V3Tristate.cpp:1158: Unlinked
                                     : ... In instance unlinkbug
  bug b(i, o);
        ^
                        ... See the manual and https://verilator.org for more assistance.
```
